{
  "stem": "2906.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they put us there to-- to stay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't even know where-- where it was because they send you away, you don't know where you are.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one day, I couldn't go to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I feel like if I go out, I'll I'll die there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very cold, and I didn't eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said to the two girls, I don't want to go out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- today I will stay without food, but I cannot go and work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they brought me food at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The two girls.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This-- the foreman came in to this couple.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the-- the man said to the foreman, you very nice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She didn't work you gave her food to eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, what?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She didn't work?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Tomorrow I'm not going to give you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You work.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Second day I had to work, and he wouldn't give me anything to eat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after this, we came back to this-- to this kolkhoz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we had a friend in Turkestan and she said to us, if you come here-- because if you [? eat ?] kolkhoz, you'll die from hunger, from-- from everything.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Did she write to you?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somebody came with a wagon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She sent a letter to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody will give you a ticket.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You cannot get a ticket to go on a train and go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Especially we were, you know, refugees from where, but we decided to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I think I had a little--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She said if you'll come here you'll survive better than-- she was afraid to-- to write too much, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- if you catch them they-- We took a train, we were four of us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we got on the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, this was a train.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
